{"about_the_game":"As Dangoru the Dragon Merchant you\u2019ll explore the enchanted Wandering Forest and befriend its inhabitants, who will join you on your adventures. Gather resources from the forest to craft items, brew magical potions, and cook delicious meals for your friends as you learn more about the mysterious Shard of Elderlight.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672180/extras/Gif1.gif?t=1684156501\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Befriend and journey with the forest\u2019s quirky creatures and send them on quests.<br></li><li>Gather resources, find recipes, craft magical items and potions.<br></li><li>Make delicious meals in your babbling cauldron!<br></li><li>Explore a fantastical, ever-shifting forest full of secrets.<br></li><li>Talk to and build relationships with fantastical forest-dwellers to help them heal and rebuild the woods.<br></li><li>Re-establish trade and commerce in the forest.<br></li><li>Unlock secrets of the forest with the Shard of Elderlight.<br></li><li>Discover the history of the Wandering Forest.</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672180/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1684156501","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672180/page.bg.jpg?t=1684156501","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672180/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1684156501","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672180/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1684156501","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"As Dangoru the Dragon Merchant you\u2019ll explore the enchanted Wandering Forest and befriend its inhabitants, who will join you on y